<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<section class="article-header py-5 bg-light border-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-10 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
                <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="mb-3">
                    <ol class="breadcrumb justify-content-center">
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/blogs" class="text-orange text-decoration-none">Blog</a></li>
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Achievement</li>
                    </ol>
                </nav>
                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-navy mb-4">Students of Blossom World Honoured for Outstanding Achievement</h1>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-muted gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="bi bi-calendar3 me-2 text-orange"></i> 10 June 2025
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="bi bi-person-circle me-2 text-orange"></i> By Admin
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="bi bi-award-fill me-2 text-orange"></i> Excellence Awards
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-5">
            
            <div class="col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-right">
                <div class="featured-img-container mb-5 rounded-4 shadow-sm overflow-hidden border">
                    <img src="/img/banner8.jpeg" class="img-fluid w-100" alt="Student Awards Ceremony">
                </div>

                <div class="article-content fs-5 text-dark-emphasis">
                    <p class="lead fw-normal">Blossom World Senior Secondary School proudly celebrated the achievements of its students during a special award ceremony held in the presence of respected dignitaries, teachers, and parents.</p>
                    
                    <p>The event was organised to recognise academic excellence, discipline, and overall performance of our students. Our students were felicitated with trophies and certificates for their remarkable accomplishments.</p>

                    <blockquote class="my-5 p-4 border-start border-5 border-orange bg-light rounded-end italic shadow-sm">
                        <p class="mb-0 fs-4">"The encouragement and guidance provided by our teachers played a vital role in shaping these achievements."</p>
                    </blockquote>

                    <p>Their confident presence on stage and sense of pride reflected the strong values and quality education imparted at Blossom World. The ceremony served as a moment of inspiration for all students, motivating them to strive for excellence in academics as well as co-curricular activities.</p>
                    
                    <p>The presence of esteemed guests added grace to the occasion and reinforced the importance of recognising talent and hard work. At Blossom World Senior Secondary School, we firmly believe that acknowledging student achievements builds confidence, responsibility, and a lifelong love for learning.</p>

                    <p>We congratulate our students on their success and wish them continued growth and excellence in the future.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="event-gallery mt-5 pt-4 border-top" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold text-navy mb-4"><i class="bi bi-images me-2 text-orange"></i>Glimpses of the Ceremony</h3>
                    <div class="row g-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                            <div class="gallery-item rounded-3 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
                                <img src="/img/banner8.jpeg" class="img-fluid w-100" style="height: 250px; object-fit: cover;">
                                <div class="gallery-overlay d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <span class="text-white fw-bold">Flag Hoisting</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                            <div class="gallery-item rounded-3 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
                                <img src="/img/gallary2.jpeg" class="img-fluid w-100" style="height: 250px; object-fit: cover;">
                                <div class="gallery-overlay d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <span class="text-white fw-bold"><a href="/updates/blogs/independence-day" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Independence Day Celebration</a></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            <div class="gallery-item rounded-3 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
                                <img src="/img/banner5.jpeg" class="img-fluid w-100" style="height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
                                <div class="gallery-overlay d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <span class="text-white fw-bold"><a href="/updates/blogs/republic-day" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Republic Day Celebration</a></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-light p-4 rounded-4 d-flex align-items-center shadow-sm my-5">
                    <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Admin&background=001f3f&color=fff" class="rounded-circle me-4 border border-3 border-white shadow-sm" width="80">
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold text-navy mb-1">Blossom World Editorial</h5>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Committed to celebrating every milestone of our students.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-left">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 mb-4 rounded-4 bg-white">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-navy mb-4 border-bottom pb-2">More Events</h5>
                    <div class="recent-post-item mb-3 pb-3 border-bottom">
                        <a href="/blogs/independence-day" class="text-decoration-none">
                            <h6 class="fw-bold text-navy mb-1 hover-orange">Independence Day Celebration</h6>
                            <small class="text-muted">Aug 15, 2024</small>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="recent-post-item">
                        <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">
                            <h6 class="fw-bold text-navy mb-1 hover-orange">STEM Innovation Lab</h6>
